						               													<description>Includes new weapons, systems and skins to fight with, including but not limited to: Cluster Bombs, Infantry Pods, Electrolasers, UAVs, Super-steel Rams, Limpet Mines, and Thermal Lances.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Expansion also introduces a new type of card, the Powercore, which tracks your robot's battery level. Use your stored energy to activate the Powercore's special ability or to overcharge your electrical weaponry and unleash devastating attacks, but manage your energy levels wisely otherwise you might find your robot out of juice when you need it most.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Expansion also introduces infantry to the fray and provides rules allowing your pilots to fight on foot if their robot becomes crippled.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Ten new scenarios are included which cover new ground including solitaire, pilot rescues, orbital insertions, free-for-alls and a post-apocalyptic campaign.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Includes:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;6 Extra Vehicle Figures&amp;#10;6 Power Core Cards&amp;#10;32 Design Cards&amp;#10;20 infantry, Mine, &amp;amp; UAV Tents&amp;#10;Expansion Game Rules&amp;#10;Science Behind the Game&amp;#10;Kriegbot Errata&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
